Evidence: Loaded: bad-setting (Reason: Unit k3s.service has a bad unit file setting.)

This PR removes the problematic systemd.services.k3s override block from infra/nixos/hosts/hetzner-worker-1/default.nix, restoring the valid k3s agent configuration."}
